title: Canelo Alvarez vs Caleb Plant - THE EYES DON'T LIE
author: Motivedia - Boxing
description:
Canelo vs Plant, the history-making Super Middleweight showdown, is almost here. 
A brooding banger filled with Mexican machismo will collide with a Tennessee talent with unshakeable self-belief.. And if you're not already hyped up during fight week - here's a little breakdown of some of the finer details to get you ready for Saturdays fight!
